Package org.elasticsearch.search.aggregations.bucket.histogram

Interface DateIntervalConsumer<T>

All Known Implementing Classes:
DateHistogramAggregationBuilder, DateHistogramValuesSourceBuilder
public interface DateIntervalConsumer<T>
A shared interface for aggregations that parse and use "interval" parameters. Provides definitions for the new fixed and calendar intervals, and deprecated defintions for the old interval/dateHisto interval parameters
